{"tid":1739991,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"突發！某區狗宿有大獲嘢發生！","createTime":"2019-11-19T20:55:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-20T09:42:20.000Z","uid":340987,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"039da309e63dbcc77bef1e51fddcfcde8089da26","tid":1739991,"uid":340987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T20:55:30.000Z","msg":"收到風某區狗宿有個清潔工清潔廁所嗰陣好唔小心咁同時倒瀉漂白粉(calcium hypochlorite powder)同埋通渠水(HCl) 產生咗大量氯氣！<br />\n<br />\nCa(ClO)2 + 4HCl &mdash;&gt; CaCl2 + 2Cl2 + 2H2O<br />\n<br />\n而家唔知點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />氯氣好毒架麻，會死人架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但我最驚就係啲暴徒有樣學樣，戴口罩假扮清潔工入去搞事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95596b7f11c52fc3655bca6b4ae8b136b9f38510","tid":1739991,"uid":340987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"039da309e63dbcc77bef1e51fddcfcde8089da26","tid":1739991,"uid":340987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T20:55:30.000Z","msg":"收到風某區狗宿有個清潔工清潔廁所嗰陣好唔小心咁同時倒瀉漂白粉(calcium hypochlorite powder)同埋通渠水(HCl) 產生咗大量氯氣！<br />\n<br />\nCa(ClO)2 + 4HCl &mdash;&gt; CaCl2 + 2Cl2 + 2H2O<br />\n<br />\n而家唔知點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />氯氣好毒架麻，會死人架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但我最驚就係啲暴徒有樣學樣，戴口罩假扮清潔工入去搞事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T20:57:22.000Z","msg":"千其唔好咁做呀 好危險架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4134d61e790ede0a768f327fe3312d24a1f9dc21","tid":1739991,"uid":44870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T20:57:52.000Z","msg":"幫下你個閪佬推"},{"pid":"842181ca1ce9c8967353043ce8e7c401339346ab","tid":1739991,"uid":49336,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T20:58:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ruOwWnv.png\" data-thumbnail-s